                "item_values": [],
                "key": "The Way of Sunfire",
                "string_values": [
                  "<p>After a Charged Attack hits an opponent, a Sunfire Arrow will descend upon the opponent hit, dealing <span style=\"color: rgb(55, 255, 255)\">60%/75%/90%/105%/120%</span> ATK as DMG, and applying the Heartsearer effect to the opponent damaged by said Arrow for 10s. Opponents affected by Heartsearer take <span style=\"color: rgb(55, 255, 255)\">28%/35%/42%/49%/56%</span> more Charged Attack DMG from the wielder. A Sunfire Arrow can be triggered once every 10s.</p>"
                ]
              },
              {
